imdb.plot outline: The world has been ravaged by zombie warfare. Two dictators took charge and created two militaristic nations warring over scarce resources. Zombies surround city borders. Free thought has been eliminated. Newborns are drafted into military or research programs. Alex, Jamie, Nick, and Jeremy are students of the University of State 2 residing in a volatile border state, and the only people who can save the world from destruction is - no one. No one cares. Alex and crew just want to get by and graduate.
